Description: USB LCD System Monitor Driver and GUI
 USB LCD driver and GUI application for displaying real-time system
 information on compatible USB LCD displays.
 .
 Features include:
  - Customizable text positioning and styling
  - CPU, GPU, memory, and disk monitoring
  - Background image/video support
  - Drag-and-drop interface for layout customization
  - System tray integration with minimize-to-tray support